From: art-suite conda packaging
Subject: [PATCH] Add missing <cstdint> and <limits> includes

A few art TUs use fixed-width integer types ([u]intN_t) or std::numeric_limits
without the owning header. Newer libstdc++ no longer leaks these transitively.
Add the direct includes (IWYU). Non-test TUs only. Generated against the tree
with 0001-0003 applied. See potential_improvements.md.

--- a/art/Framework/Services/Optional/TimeTracker_service.cc	2026-06-19 12:36:48.229687409 -0700
+++ b/art/Framework/Services/Optional/TimeTracker_service.cc	2026-06-19 12:36:48.233687468 -0700
@@ -1,6 +1,7 @@
 // vim: set sw=2 expandtab :
 
